<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Design Submission Received</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .design-box { background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #38ef7d; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #38ef7d; color: #111; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸŽ¨ Design Submission Received</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
      
      <p>Thank you! Your design for <strong>"{{productTitle}}"</strong> has been received and is now under review.</p>
      
      <div class="design-box">
        <strong>Submission Details:</strong><br>
        <strong>Design Title:</strong> {{designTitle}}<br>
        <strong>Submitted:</strong> {{submittedDate}}<br>
        <strong>Files:</strong> {{fileCount}} file(s)
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>What happens next:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Our team will review your design within 3-5 business days</li>
        <li>The customer will also provide feedback</li>
        <li>You'll receive notifications about their response</li>
        <li>Iterate and improve based on feedback if needed</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>We appreciate your careful work and attention to detail!</p>
      
      <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="cta-button">{{actionLabel}}</a>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666;">
        Questions about your submission? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Engel Fine Design. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
